{"tid":772109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷：陳帆應問責下台","createTime":"2018-08-08T13:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T14:50:10.000Z","uid":92301,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e58ae91bf16e212c9e1be71a2c63779508ed33f4","tid":772109,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表示，政府跟進港鐵沙中線紅磡站月台工程圖則發現有嚴重偏差，已要求港鐵解除相關工程項目管理人員的職務。<br />\n<br />\n立法會鐵路事宜小組委員林卓廷表示，現時港鐵公信力已盪然無存，港鐵撤換高層雖然是是合理補救措施，但當前急務是鑿開出現問題工程的地方檢查，如發現出現嚴重問題應重做，又認為陳帆應問責下台。<br />\n<br />\n小組另一委員譚文豪質疑港鐵涉及造假，促政府徹查是否包括利益輸送，並追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1910180/林卓廷%3A陳帆應問責下台\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1910180%2F%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%253A%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86%E6%87%89%E5%95%8F%E8%B2%AC%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%B0&d=O%2B%2FmjTQdNMYEhUtediYwEqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=a289f088\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1910180/林卓廷%3A陳帆應問責下台</a>"},{"pid":"712a6ccdb15a32bba592edae06be52f4f4f1a76d","tid":772109,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"&quot;留低比問責需要更大勇氣&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193858934beb9c53a520eb3e492989b391418898","tid":772109,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"咁快俾佢走咪益咗佢"},{"pid":"9e4f348be5ad977b2226d0482b43136c1a2c4f41","tid":772109,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"下台啦柒頭"},{"pid":"5bd2c03a97cad22aa5e0954b468901579cbb905c","tid":772109,"uid":92301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 會員"}]}